&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a proactive and customer-focused Business Systems Analyst to support daily order management, customer coordination, warehouse operations, ERP system activities, and basic EDI support across multiple customers, vendors, and distribution partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role serves as a critical link between customers, sales, warehouses, logistics providers, accounting, and internal operations teams to ensure orders, shipments, inventory, and customer requests are processed accurately and efficiently. The ideal candidate is highly organized, analytical, and capable of managing multiple priorities in a fast-paced environment while delivering excellent customer support.&lt;/p&gt;
