&lt;h4 data-section-id=&quot;ihdyl0&quot; data-start=&quot;803&quot; data-end=&quot;840&quot;&gt;Customer Service &amp;amp; Account Support&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;841&quot; data-end=&quot;1406&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1uygakx&quot; data-start=&quot;841&quot; data-end=&quot;948&quot;&gt;Serve as a primary point of contact for customer order inquiries, shipping updates, and issue resolution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1hpndip&quot; data-start=&quot;949&quot; data-end=&quot;1074&quot;&gt;Coordinate with customers, warehouses, and carriers to resolve shipment discrepancies, missing orders, and delivery issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;jru2fo&quot; data-start=&quot;1075&quot; data-end=&quot;1146&quot;&gt;Support onboarding of new customers, vendors, and warehouse partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1cmd4m8&quot; data-start=&quot;1147&quot; data-end=&quot;1228&quot;&gt;Maintain strong working relationships with customers and internal stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1jtx2yc&quot; data-start=&quot;1229&quot; data-end=&quot;1307&quot;&gt;Respond promptly to operational issues and escalate concerns when necessary.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1lih5t4&quot; data-start=&quot;1308&quot; data-end=&quot;1406&quot;&gt;Assist with customer-specific requirements, retailer compliance, and order management processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
