&lt;h3&gt;Culinary Development &amp;amp; Innovation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive culinary development of new flavor profiles and products for assigned segments of the Kinder’s portfolio (e.g., sauces, seasonings)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate consumer insights, market trends, and retailer needs into differentiated, flavor-forward concepts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and iterate recipes from bench-top prototypes to culinary gold-standard formulations ready for scale-up and transition to R&amp;amp;D/Product Development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all formulations meet Kinder’s standards for flavor, quality, and manufacturability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support internal tastings, cuttings, and competitive benchmarking to inform product direction and refinement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with R&amp;amp;D/Product Development to support product evaluation, sensory documentation, and readiness for commercialization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
